<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Activate Your Seller Account</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        color: #333;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #2563eb;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 32px;
      }

      .content p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .otp-box {
        margin: 24px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .otp {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 32px;
        letter-spacing: 6px;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 12px 24px;
        background-color: #f1f5f9;
        border-radius: 6px;
        color: #2563eb;
      }

      .note {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #6b7280;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Activate Your Seller Account</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          Welcome to our platform! You are just one step away from becoming an
          active seller. Please use the verification code below to activate your
          seller account and start managing your store.
        </p>

        <div class="otp-box">
          <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        </div>

        <p>
          This activation code will expire shortly for security purposes. Please
          enter the code on the verification page to complete your seller
          account activation.
        </p>

        <p class="note">
          If you did not create a seller account, please ignore this email.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
